{"tid":906834,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇Reddit 班鬼佬屌緊value 新作-《artifact》嘅商業模式？","createTime":"2018-11-18T10:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T00:45:36.000Z","uid":90,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2794163aa1f97bcad34f9cd673f2749c75181e","tid":906834,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:14:30.000Z","msg":"1.  廿蚊美金隻game，冇免費卡包之外（唔計買送個10pack ），每包卡收你兩蚊美金。<br />\n<br />\n2. 你要畀錢打ranking（買入場卷） ,五美金 for 五張入場卷。而且個機制好濕鳩<br />\n<br />\n  -至少贏三場先贏返入場卷<br />\n -贏四場攞一包卡包<br />\n -贏五場攞兩包<br />\n -但輸兩場就收檔<br />\n<br />\n啲友仲擔心，如果大家肯埋單接受呢種商業模式<br />\n其他廠見搞得咁成功，就會有樣學樣<br />\n最後大家荷包受苦<br />\n<br />\nReddit 已經見到部分人呼籲退款，向value抗議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家點睇？"},{"pid":"4b12818a2acc88c504c73f270ddd535df83eef7c","tid":906834,"uid":90,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"仲有新手英都會喺卡包入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179272f53df4ea40d8e1a3b38fc75ed4056bbe11","tid":906834,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:25:06.000Z","msg":"唔比錢打ranking 仲有咩可以玩"},{"pid":"62cf764e5822c101a3caa6b9fd5176e1fc1f3610","tid":906834,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"179272f53df4ea40d8e1a3b38fc75ed4056bbe11","tid":906834,"uid":122264,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:25:06.000Z","msg":"唔比錢打ranking 仲有咩可以玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:28:25.000Z","msg":"社交模式=自訂 <br />\n休閒模式= 打AI + 普通PVP+ 車輪戰"},{"pid":"139cdea03691930cafa42f7fa92b8cf09c2d0383","tid":906834,"uid":2772,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"value?"},{"pid":"c0f2b92917274f0fd3557133cef929ecac89cef5","tid":906834,"uid":157994,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"手機課金、ea擠牙膏都維持到，<br />\n<br />\n而且仲要大賺過俾心機製作既indie g